For DBMail 2.1
-   Database table prefixes
-   Sieve scripting language
-   header caching (cache headers like To: From: etc.)
-   Fix wrong order of headers when doing a FETCH MSGNUM (RFC822.HEADER)
-   put (part of) configuration into the database
-   Increase speed by doing database optimizations (indexes) and removing
    unneeded database usage.

